-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 NDSPMHD: A Smoothed Particle (Magneto)Hydrodynamics code for (astrophysical)
 fluid dynamics simulations in 1, 2 and 3 spatial dimensions.

 (c) 2002-2015 Daniel Price
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

